<header>
  <a class="hdr-logo-link" href="../index.html" title="Zurück zum Englisch-Lernzentrum"><img src="../assets/logo_hellweg.png" alt="Logo der Hellweg-Realschule Unna-Massen" style="cursor:pointer"/></a>
  <h1>ZAP – Tenses Wiederholung</h1>
  <p class="sub">Simple Present · Simple Past · Will Future · Welche Zeit passt?</p>
</header>

<div class="container">
  <section class="rules-combined">
    <div class="quiz-divider" style="margin:0 0 16px"><span>⚡ Die drei Zeitformen auf einen Blick</span></div>
    <div class="note" style="margin-bottom:16px">Hier die <b>drei wichtigsten Zeiten</b> für die ZAP. Erst kurz wiederholen, dann unten üben.</div>
    <div class="rc-grid">

      <div class="rc-card c-green">
        <div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
        <div class="rc-card-num">1</div>
        <div class="rc-card-body">
          <div class="rc-card-label">🟢 Simple Present</div>
          <div class="rc-formula">
            <span class="fc fc-subj">Subj.</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-verb">Grundform</span></span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">(+</span><span class="fc fc-s">s</span></span><span class="fc-punct">)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rc-rule"><b>he / she / it</b> bekommt ein <b>-s</b> am Verb.<br>Verneinung: <b>don't / doesn't</b> + Grundform.<br>Frage: <b>Do / Does</b> + Subj. + Grundform?<br><b>Verwendung:</b> Gewohnheiten, Fakten, regelmäßige Handlungen, Stundenpläne.<br><b>Signalwörter:</b> every day, often, usually, always, never, sometimes.</div>
          <div class="rc-examples-new">
            I <span class="hl-verb">play</span> tennis every Monday.<br>
            She <span class="hl-verb">works</span> in Bonn.<br>
            They <span class="hl-neg">don't</span> <span class="hl-verb">like</span> tea.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rc-card c-amber">
        <div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
        <div class="rc-card-num">2</div>
        <div class="rc-card-body">
          <div class="rc-card-label">🟡 Simple Past</div>
          <div class="rc-formula">
            <span class="fc fc-subj">Subj.</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-verb">Verb-ed / past participle</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="rc-rule"><b>regelmäßig:</b> Verb + <b>-ed</b> (work → worked).<br><b>unregelmäßig:</b> eigene Form (go → went, see → saw, buy → bought).<br>Verneinung: <b>didn't</b> + Grundform. Frage: <b>Did</b> + Subj. + Grundform?<br><b>Verwendung:</b> abgeschlossene Handlung in der Vergangenheit – mit klarer Zeit.<br><b>Signalwörter:</b> yesterday, last week, in 2020, … ago, when.</div>
          <div class="rc-examples-new">
            We <span class="hl-verb">watched</span> a film <span class="hl-sig">yesterday</span>.<br>
            She <span class="hl-verb">went</span> to London <span class="hl-sig">last summer</span>.<br>
            They <span class="hl-neg">didn't</span> <span class="hl-verb">help</span> me.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rc-card c-blue">
        <div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
        <div class="rc-card-num">3</div>
        <div class="rc-card-body">
          <div class="rc-card-label">🔵 Will Future</div>
          <div class="rc-formula">
            <span class="fc fc-subj">Subj.</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-do">will</span></span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-verb">Grundform</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="rc-rule"><b>will</b> + <b>Grundform</b> – für <b>alle</b> Personen gleich.<br>Verneinung: <b>won't</b> (= will not). Frage: <b>Will</b> + Subj. + Grundform?<br><b>Verwendung:</b> spontane Entscheidungen, Vorhersagen, Versprechen, allgemeine Zukunft.<br><b>Signalwörter:</b> tomorrow, next week, in 2030, soon, in the future, I think / I hope / probably.</div>
          <div class="rc-examples-new">
            I <span class="hl-do">will</span> <span class="hl-verb">help</span> you <span class="hl-sig">tomorrow</span>.<br>
            She <span class="hl-do">will</span> <span class="hl-verb">be</span> 16 <span class="hl-sig">next year</span>.<br>
            We <span class="hl-neg">won't</span> <span class="hl-verb">forget</span> this trip.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rc-card c-teal">
        <div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
        <div class="rc-card-num">4</div>
        <div class="rc-card-body">
          <div class="rc-card-label">📌 Welche Zeit passt? – Signalwörter</div>
          <div class="rc-formula" style="gap:5px 4px;flex-wrap:wrap">
            <span class="fc-tz">every day · usually · often → SP</span>
            <span class="fc-tz">yesterday · ago · last … → Past</span>
            <span class="fc-tz">tomorrow · next … · I think → Will</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rc-rule">An den <b>Signalwörtern</b> erkennst du die Zeit.<br><b>Simple Present:</b> regelmäßig, jetzt allgemein gültig.<br><b>Simple Past:</b> klar abgeschlossen, in der Vergangenheit.<br><b>Will Future:</b> noch nicht passiert, später.<br><span style="font-size:12px">⚠️ <b>since / for / just / already / yet</b> → Present Perfect, NICHT diese drei Zeiten.</span></div>
          <div class="rc-examples-new">
            I <span class="hl-sig">always</span> <span class="hl-verb">eat</span> breakfast at seven. (SP)<br>
            We <span class="hl-verb">moved</span> here <span class="hl-sig">in 2020</span>. (Past)<br>
            They <span class="hl-do">will</span> <span class="hl-verb">come</span> <span class="hl-sig">tomorrow</span>. (Will)
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="quiz-divider"><span>✏️ Übungen zur ZAP-Wiederholung</span></div>

  <details class="accordion" id="acc-sp">
    <summary><span class="acc-num">1</span>🟢 Simple Present üben</summary>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="note">Wiederholung: Aussagesätze (he/she/it + s), Verneinung (don't / doesn't), Fragen (Do / Does …?), Signalwörter.</div>
      <div class="progress-wrap" id="sp-progress"><div class="progress" role="progressbar" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><div class="progress-fill" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg,#16a34a,#4ade80)"></div></div><div class="progress-text">Fortschritt: 0/15 richtig (0%)</div></div>
      <div class="section-actions"><button class="btn green" id="sp-check-all">Alle prüfen</button><button class="btn gray" id="sp-reset">Zurücksetzen</button><button class="btn ghost" id="sp-reroll">🎲 Neu würfeln</button></div>
      <div id="sp-tasks"></div>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="accordion" id="acc-past">
    <summary><span class="acc-num">2</span>🟡 Simple Past üben</summary>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="note">Wiederholung: regelmäßige (-ed) und unregelmäßige Verben, was/were, didn't + Grundform, Did …?, Signalwörter.</div>
      <div class="progress-wrap" id="past-progress"><div class="progress" role="progressbar" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><div class="progress-fill" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg,#d4a017,#f59e0b)"></div></div><div class="progress-text">Fortschritt: 0/15 richtig (0%)</div></div>
      <div class="section-actions"><button class="btn" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#d4a017,#f59e0b);color:#fff;" id="past-check-all">Alle prüfen</button><button class="btn gray" id="past-reset">Zurücksetzen</button><button class="btn ghost" id="past-reroll">🎲 Neu würfeln</button></div>
      <div id="past-tasks"></div>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="accordion" id="acc-wf">
    <summary><span class="acc-num">3</span>🔵 Will Future üben</summary>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="note">Wiederholung: will + Grundform für alle Personen, won't (= will not), Will …?, Signalwörter (tomorrow, next …, I think …).</div>
      <div class="progress-wrap" id="wf-progress"><div class="progress blue" role="progressbar" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><div class="progress-fill"></div></div><div class="progress-text">Fortschritt: 0/15 richtig (0%)</div></div>
      <div class="section-actions"><button class="btn blue" id="wf-check-all">Alle prüfen</button><button class="btn gray" id="wf-reset">Zurücksetzen</button><button class="btn ghost" id="wf-reroll">🎲 Neu würfeln</button></div>
      <div id="wf-tasks"></div>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="accordion" id="acc-mix">
    <summary><span class="acc-num">4</span>🎯 Welche Zeit passt? (Mixed)</summary>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="note"><b>Die ZAP-Aufgabe:</b> Die richtige Zeitform wählen.<br><b>Stufe 1:</b> Zeit erkennen (MC) · <b>Stufe 2:</b> Lücken füllen · <b>Stufe 3:</b> Korrigieren / Übersetzen.</div>
      <div class="level-switch" id="mix-levels"><button data-level="1" class="active">🟢 Erkennen</button><button data-level="2">🟡 Lücken</button><button data-level="3">🔴 Transfer</button></div>
      <div class="progress-wrap" id="mix-progress"><div class="progress" role="progressbar" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><div class="progress-fill" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg,#7c2d12,#b85c20)"></div></div><div class="progress-text">Fortschritt: 0/15 richtig (0%)</div></div>
      <div class="section-actions"><button class="btn" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c2d12,#b85c20);color:#fff;" id="mix-check-all">Alle prüfen</button><button class="btn gray" id="mix-reset">Zurücksetzen</button><button class="btn ghost" id="mix-reroll">🎲 Neu würfeln</button></div>
      <div id="mix-tasks"></div>
    </div>
  </details>

  <div class="quiz-divider"><span>🤖 KI-Tutor</span></div>
  <details class="accordion" id="acc-ki">
    <summary><span class="acc-num">🤖</span>KI-Tutor – Frag mich zu den drei Zeitformen</summary>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="ki-wrap">
        <div class="ki-welcome">
          <strong>👋 Hallo! Ich bin dein KI-Tutor für die ZAP-Wiederholung.</strong><br>
          Ich helfe dir bei <b>Simple Present</b>, <b>Simple Past</b> und <b>Will Future</b>. Stell mir Fragen zur Bildung, zur Verwendung oder schick mir einen Satz zum Prüfen. Tipps gibt's – fertige Lösungen nicht!
          <div class="ki-badges">
            <span class="ki-badge">Simple Present</span>
            <span class="ki-badge">Simple Past</span>
            <span class="ki-badge">Will Future</span>
            <span class="ki-badge">Signalwörter</span>
            <span class="ki-badge">Welche Zeit passt?</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ki-chips">
          <button class="ki-chip" onclick="kiSend(this.textContent)">Welche Zeit passt: I ___ to school every day?</button>
